      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 48,
      "message": "Consider:\n\n public class SanMapper implements Function<String, ValidatedSan> {\n    @Override\n    public ValidatedSan apply(String san) {\n        if (isEmailAddressValid(san)) {\n            return new ValidatedSan(san, GeneralName.rfc822Name);\n        } else if (isIpAddressValid(san)) {\n            return new ValidatedSan(san, GeneralName.iPAddress);\n        } else if (isDomainNameValid(san)) {\n            return new ValidatedSan(san, GeneralName.dNSName);\n        } else {\n            throw new CsrConfigurationException(\"San :\" + san + \" does not match any requirements\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n\nOr some form like that.",
      "author": {
